SetInCountry: India
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Vanessa Treesa Jimmy
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "Reine threw the phone onto the bed and screamed. Her boss had just added to\
  \ the piled up work for the weekend. If only she could have some time for herself\
  \ and travel someplace! \nShe had enough money by now, only courage was lacking\
  \ to go on a journey which would change her life altogether."
